CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 16, 1946, pg. 3, reads: "Celebrants - These members of the 'Carmen Jones' [text cut off] ... attended the wedding reception for Mr. and Mrs. Kenneth Bacon (Eurylee Leonardis) [Urylee Leonardos] Friday night. Left to right: Ruth Crumpton, Dorothy McDavid, Elton Warren and Coreanna [Coreania] Hayman. - Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Actors, cast members of "Carmen Jones," from left: Ruth Crumpton, Dorothy McDavid, Elton Warren, and Coreania Hayman posed in interior at wedding reception for Urylee Leonardos and Kenneth Bacon
